# Project 7 - Troubleshooting & Verification Lab

## Objective
Validate connectivity across VLANs and multiple sites using routing and OSPF.

## Tests Performed
- Local VLAN communication
- Inter-VLAN routing
- Remote site connectivity
- DHCP verification
- Routing table validation
- OSPF neighbor verification

## Tools Used
- Cisco Packet Tracer
- CLI commands (ping, ipconfig, show ip route, show ip ospf neighbor)

## Result
All devices successfully communicate across VLANs and sites.
OSPF neighbors are in FULL state and routing tables are correctly populated.
